Semantic Cache Architecture Flow. User Query -> Embedding Model -> Vector Search -> Hit/Miss Decision (Threshold 0.92). Hit: Cached Response -> Return. Miss: LLM Call -> Store in Cache -> Return. Cache Store: Embeddings Array + Responses Array + Queries Array. TTL Management. Cosine Similarity computation. Threshold impact table: 0.95=10-15%, 0.92=20-30%, 0.88=30-40%, 0.85=40-50% hit rates with risk annotations. Clean flow diagram.